================ TF-IDF CONCEPT ================

30. TF (Term Frequency)
Measures how frequently a word appears in a document.

Formula:

:contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}

31. IDF (Inverse Document Frequency)
Measures importance of word.

Formula:

:contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}

Purpose of log:
- reduces very large values
- smoothens scaling

32. TF-IDF Formula

:contentReference[oaicite:2]{index=2}

High TF-IDF:
Word is important in that document.

Low TF-IDF:
Word is common across documents.



